    <TaskName>Jared and Oprah</TaskName>
    <TaskDescription>
        Suppose Jared is a diet tester for Oprah Winfrey.  He eats exactly what 
        she eats, and does the same exercises too. He and Oprah compare weights 
        each week, and it turns out that Jared is always 50 pounds heavier than 
        Oprah.  Create a model of Jared’s weight. A node representing Oprah’s 
        weight has already been created for you. 
    </TaskDescription>
    <URL>images/jared-and-oprah.jpg</URL>
    <StartTime>0</StartTime>
    <EndTime>10</EndTime>
    <Units>Days</Units>
    <NodeCount>3</NodeCount>
